<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ARTLANG IN DIR CH480</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Fing le tlang sang par in a thang, Thawngtha muko tum thawng cu, Ngai
 u, hla thiang sak thawng a thang, Kan caah thawngtha a si.

[C1]
   Artlang in dir, raldo awkah, artlang in dir, raldo awkah, chuak u,
   (chuak u, chuak u,) muko thawng a thang, (muko thawng ngai u), chuak u,
   chuak u, (chuak u, chuak u), Khrihfa ralkap hna, chuak u, (Khrihfa ralkap
   hna chuak u.

[V2]
 Siangpahrang ralthuam i hruk u, Teinak puanlang cu lek u, Biatak le
 dinnak cu tanh u, Vanmi nih an kan cuanh ko.

[C2]
   Artlang in dir, raldo awkah, artlang in dir, raldo awkah, chuak u,
   (chuak u, chuak u,) muko thawng a thang, (muko thawng ngai u), chuak u,
   chuak u, (chuak u, chuak u), Khrihfa ralkap hna, chuak u, (Khrihfa ralkap
   hna chuak u.

[V3]
 Nan ngun muko cu tum rih u, Ral donak aan sang chin seh, Zeizong Jesuh
 ca si dingin, Nunnak pek in kan tei lai.

[C3]
   Artlang in dir, raldo awkah, artlang in dir, raldo awkah, chuak u,
   (chuak u, chuak u,) muko thawng a thang, (muko thawng ngai u), chuak u,
   chuak u, (chuak u, chuak u), Khrihfa ralkap hna, chuak u, (Khrihfa ralkap
   hna chuak u.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>480</hymn_number>
</song>